@dougyphresh-
If the subs in a rar file, you need to extract them first into the same folder that the movie is in.
I use VLC media player, which has a drop-down menu,(usually easier to find without a skin) that asks you to choose a file, that's it. Other media players should be similar. Check TPB's forum, suprbay.org, there is a link at the bottom of this page, for more info.
